VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT WebView.*setJavaScriptEnabled\(true\)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:setJavaScriptEnabled\s*\(\s*true && MISSING:setAllowFileAccess\s*\(\s*false|setSafeBrowsingEnabled\s*\(\s*true|setWebViewClient|shouldOverrideUrlLoading
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects insecure WebView configurations that enable JavaScript.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Insecure WebView Configuration.
